# 06.06 CI/CD Pipeline

## Overview

The CI/CD Pipeline defines how cmdOS source code is automatically built, tested, validated, and delivered through a continuous software development process.

Because cmdOS is an AI Execution Operating System with multiple interconnected components, a reliable CI/CD system is required to maintain:

- Development speed
- System stability
- Code quality
- Security
- Deployment reliability

Core principle:

Code Change

↓

Build

↓

Test

↓

Validate

↓

Deploy

↓

Monitor

---

# 1. CI/CD Pipeline Purpose

The purpose of the CI/CD Pipeline is to automate the software delivery lifecycle of cmdOS.

It enables:

- Automated code validation
- Faster development cycles
- Consistent releases
- Reduced deployment errors
- Continuous improvement

